verses.text: \w To|strong="H0623"\w* you, O God, we give praise, \w to|strong="H0623"\w* you we give praise: \w and|strong="H0623"\w* those who give honour \w to|strong="H0623"\w* your name make clear your works of power.

When \w the|strong="H8034"\w* right time \w has|strong="H0430"\w* come, \w I|strong="H8034"\w* \w will|strong="H0430"\w* \w be|strong="H8034"\w* \w the|strong="H8034"\w* judge \w in|strong="H0430"\w* righteousness.

\w When|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* earth \w and|strong="H3947"\w* all \w its|strong="H3947"\w* people become feeble, \w I|strong="H0589"\w* \w am|strong="H0589"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* support \w of|strong="H8199"\w* \w its|strong="H3947"\w* pillars. (Selah.)

\w I|strong="H0595"\w* say \w to|strong="H0776"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w men|strong="H3605"\w* \w of|strong="H0776"\w* pride, Let \w your|strong="H3605"\w* pride \w be|strong="H0776"\w* gone: \w and|strong="H0776"\w* \w to|strong="H0776"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* sinners, Let \w not|strong="H0776"\w* \w your|strong="H3605"\w* horn \w be|strong="H0776"\w* lifted \w up|strong="H3605"\w*.

\w Let|strong="H0408"\w* \w not|strong="H0408"\w* \w your|strong="H0559"\w* \w horn|strong="H7161"\w* \w be|strong="H0408"\w* \w lifted|strong="H7311"\w* \w up|strong="H7311"\w*: \w let|strong="H0408"\w* \w no|strong="H0408"\w* \w more|strong="H7563"\w* words \w of|strong="H7161"\w* pride come from \w your|strong="H0559"\w* outstretched necks.

\w For|strong="H7311"\w* honour does \w not|strong="H0408"\w* come from \w the|strong="H1696"\w* east, \w or|strong="H0408"\w* from \w the|strong="H1696"\w* west, \w or|strong="H0408"\w* uplifting from \w the|strong="H1696"\w* south;

\w But|strong="H3588"\w* \w God|strong="H3808"\w* \w is|strong="H3808"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* judge, putting \w down|strong="H3588"\w* \w one|strong="H3808"\w*, \w and|strong="H7311"\w* \w lifting|strong="H7311"\w* \w up|strong="H7311"\w* \w another|strong="H3808"\w*.

\w For|strong="H3588"\w* \w in|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* hand \w of|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* Lord \w is|strong="H2088"\w* \w a|strong="H3588"\w* cup, \w and|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* wine \w is|strong="H2088"\w* red; \w it|strong="H3588"\w* \w is|strong="H2088"\w* well mixed, overflowing \w from|strong="H0430"\w* \w his|strong="H3588"\w* hand: \w he|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H0430"\w* \w make|strong="H7311"\w* all \w the|strong="H3588"\w* sinners \w of|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* earth \w take|strong="H7311"\w* \w of|strong="H0430"\w* \w it|strong="H3588"\w*, \w even|strong="H3588"\w* \w to|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* last drop.

\w But|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w ever|strong="H2088"\w* \w be|strong="H3027"\w* \w full|strong="H4392"\w* \w of|strong="H0776"\w* joy, \w making|strong="H3605"\w* songs \w of|strong="H0776"\w* \w praise|strong="H3588"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w of|strong="H0776"\w* Jacob.

\w By|strong="H0430"\w* \w him|strong="H5046"\w* \w will|strong="H0430"\w* \w all|strong="H5769"\w* \w the|strong="H0589"\w* horns \w of|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H0589"\w* sinners \w be|strong="H0430"\w* cut off; \w but|strong="H3290"\w* \w the|strong="H0589"\w* horns \w of|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H0589"\w* upright \w will|strong="H0430"\w* \w be|strong="H0430"\w* lifted \w up|strong="H0589"\w*.
